name: Strikethrough (EvilStar Studios)
description:
You're a time-manipulating ninja with the job of clearing the Bats' Dungeon. You have 5 minutes. GO!

The game made in only 48 hours in 2020 for a local gamejam from Romania called "Jam de Casa"

https://web.archive.org/web/20200513080500/https://www.jamdecasa.ro/

Team:

  • Zarnot - Level design, Sound
  • Misterdll - Art
